{"type":null,"faqId":32842,"title":"如何调整所拍摄照片的大小？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、照片的大小和相机的分辨率有关，分辨率越高，照片越大。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、进入相机取景界面，点击</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=102306\" style=\"width:0.104166664in;height:0.072916664in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，然后点击“设置 &gt; 分辨率”，调整相机的分辨率。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、通过“图库”或其他第三方应用打开已拍摄的照片，通过对照片进行修剪，也可以改变照片大小。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7562","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748427000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":8,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"调整,照片,大小","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}